snaky
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:
Definition:ill-tempered; irritable; angry espec. Go snaky, to become angry, to turn nasty ;(occas. SNAKY-TEMPERED) [AND savage, angry 1894 go snaky 1918]
Origin:[none]
